## Consistency score derivation

```
score = 100
  - 5 × dissents_count                  ({{DISSENTS_COUNT}})
  - 3 × low_confidence_findings (<70%)  ({{LOW_CONF_COUNT}})
  - 2 × partial_status_count            ({{PARTIAL_COUNT}})
  - 10 × any_failed_simulation_scenario ({{FAILED_SIM_COUNT}})
  clamped at [0, 100]
= {{CONSISTENCY_SCORE}}
```

